<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-blue-50 to-sky-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-sky-700 drop-shadow mb-2">About <span class="text-blue-500">Dsin Manufacturing</span></h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl">Empowering innovation with precision engineering for Automotive, Industrial, Medical, and Aerospace sectors.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
      <div class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-blue-100">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline-block"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="#38bdf8"/><path d="M8 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Company Profile
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Dsin Manufacturing is a precision engineering company operating 
          in the agriculture, plantation, fabrication, industrial, and automotive sectors. We provide high-quality 
          equipment and engineering solutions designed to enhance productivity and operational reliability. 
          With modern manufacturing technology and skilled experts, we are committed to precision, quality, and innovation.</p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 via-sky-100 to-white rounded-xl p-4 mt-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-1">Vision & Mission</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700">
            <li><span class="font-bold text-sky-700">Vision:</span></li>
            <div>To become a trusted leader in precision manufacturing by delivering 
              innovative and high-quality engineering solutions across multiple industries.</div>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-sky-700">Mission:</span></li>
            <li class="ml-4">Produce high-quality precision products and equipment.</li>
            <li class="ml-4">Deliver innovative, efficient, and reliable engineering solutions.</li>
            <li class="ml-4">Build strong partnerships through professional and responsive service.</li>
            <li class="ml-4">Develop competent and integrity-driven human resources.</li>
            <li class="ml-4">Implement safe, modern, and sustainable manufacturing practices.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-sky-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-sky-600 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline-block"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="4" fill="#0ea5e9"/><path d="M8 12h8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            Core Values
          </h4>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-500">Integrity</span> in production</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-500">Customer focus</span> at every step</li>
            <li><span class="font-semibold text-blue-500">Continuous improvement</span> in all processes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-100 via-blue-50 to-white rounded-xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-1">Organization</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-700">Structured teams: <span class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Engineering</span>, <span class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Production</span>, <span class="font-semibold text-sky-700">QA</span>, <span class="font-semibold text-sky-700">Sales & Support</span>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center justify-center">
      <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border border-blue-100 w-full md:w-1/3 text-center">
        <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">1+ Years Experience</h5>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Trusted by leading brands for precision and reliability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border border-sky-100 w-full md:w-1/3 text-center">
        <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-sky-600 mb-2">Local Reach</h5>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Projects delivered across Province Indonesia</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border border-blue-100 w-full md:w-1/3 text-center">
        <h5 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Certified Quality</h5>
        <p class="text-slate-600">none.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
